name: Cubes Aren't Well Rounded
description:
This is a small 3d game where a cube just dosen't fit in. This game was made in one day for the Completion Game Jam. The first two days I overscoped to where I didn't even have the skills to make the game. So on the last day I went back to basics and made this.

Also this is my first game jam (That I finished) And Wow doing this was an AMAZING experience!
